comments: great class, interesting, fair teacher, easy grader.

Guy is great. Its easy to get a good grade in his class, and you actually can get some stuff out of this class. Very fun, talked about south park, facebook, watched loose change, the class was very enjoyable. A little bit of writing, but the class is definitely worth taking for a C and a GPA booster.
Able to keep us interested and motivated while not being a slave driver. The structure at the end of the semester was a bit confusing though.
